            <Ability name="Desert Thirst">
                <Traits>Arcane, Transmutation</Traits>
                <Description>When casting &lt;i&gt;create water&lt;/i&gt;, the dragon can attempt to destroy liquid instead of creating it, turning an equal amount of liquid into sand. This destroys liquid magic or alchemical items if they're of a lower level than the dragon (a creature can attempt a DC 32 Will save to protect all liquids in its possession). This doesn't affect the liquids in a creature's body.</Description>
