                <Description>A demilich has one permanent 8th-level &lt;i&gt;contingency&lt;/i&gt; spell in effect with one of its arcane innate spells of 5th level or lower as the companion spell— typically &lt;i&gt;dimension door&lt;/i&gt;.  The demilich ends torpor, rolls initiative, and gains the effect of its &lt;i&gt;contingency's&lt;/i&gt; companion spell. The &lt;i&gt;contingency&lt;/i&gt; resets after 24 hours.</Description>
            </Ability>
            <Ability name="Countermeasures" cost="Free">
                <Trigger>The demilich's turn begins.</Trigger>
                <Description>The demilich casts &lt;i&gt;blink&lt;/i&gt;, &lt;i&gt;fly&lt;/i&gt;, &lt;i&gt;spell turning&lt;/i&gt;, or &lt;i&gt;true seeing&lt;/i&gt; on itself. It usually chooses spell turning unless it already has that spell in effect.</Description>
