                <Description>The dragon breathes euphoric gas in a 10-foot cone. Each creature in the area must succeed at a DC 18 Fortitude save or become stupefied 2 and slowed 1 for 1d4 rounds; on a critical failure, the duration is 1 minute. The faerie dragon can't use Breath Weapon again for 1d4 rounds.</Description>
            </Ability>
