        <Description>As with any humanoid animated statues of Medium size, giant animated statues are used to guard locations of importance, but their increased size and power make them most useful in large vaults, spacious chambers, or outdoor locations. Animated objects of this strength and size are ideal for tasks and responsibilities usually performed by golems, and more powerful animated objects are thus all but unheard of.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Recall Knowledge - Construct (Arcana, Crafting)&lt;/b&gt;: DC 23</Description>
